{"word":"ὑπερέρχομαι","slug":"ὑπερέρχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑπερέρχομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> with aor2 and <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>:— <i>to pass over</i> a river, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to surpass, excel</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}